item.description:
A simple but sufficient setup to response to a review. The rev command guards that response is given and prints a red note otherwise.
main.tex:
\documentclass[a4paper,USenglish]{article} \usepackage{xcolor} \newcommand{\rev}[2]{ \item #1 \if\relax\detokenize{#2}\relax {\color{red}UNANSWERED} \else {\color{blue}#2} \fi } \begin{document} \section*{Response} We thank the reviewers for their reviews \dots \subsection*{Reviewer 1} \begin{enumerate} \rev{Line 128: \dots}{} \rev{Line 256: \dots}{we changed this} \end{enumerate} \end{document}
